text: Antrim (, )Postal Towns/Bailte Poist , Northern Ireland Place-name Project. Queen's University Belfast. Retrieved 8 March 2012. is a town and civil parish in County Antrim in the northeast of Northern Ireland. It had a population of 23,375 people in the 2011 Census. ==References== Category:County towns in Northern Ireland Category:Settlements in County Antrim
